message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with signal processing and machine learning techniques for sound detection and localization. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.CV (computer vision) as the authors use semantic segmentation on spectrograms, cs.SY (systems and control) as the paper deals with designing a system to operate robustly in an unpredictable environment, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses machine learning techniques for classification and localization, and cs.CR (cryptography and security) as the paper deals with detecting emergency sounds in an urban scenario which could have security implications.
